Let's be successful together! 

 Our Partner is strong, international manufacturing company that has sites globally. 
 We are looking for an experienced colleague for their growing IT Team. 
 For the position below: 
 Description of the open position: Support for the entire SAP CO area - in Europe; 
Adjustments in SAP CO module by means of customizing; 
Creation of functional and technical concepts for the development and implementation of SAP solutions in English; 
Design and implementation of processes and functions in rollout projects, as well as the associated customizing tasks; 
Implementation of training courses and support with integration and regression tests; 
Communication with external consultants and the associated helpdesk; 
Taking on sub-projects and communicating with key users; 
Coordination with audit companies and provision of the necessary data. The registration No. of Hire-One Ltds. is this: 3376/2008. 
 Requirements: You have professional experience in the SAP CO environment as a consultant; 
You have a successfully completed degree or comparable training, ideally with SAP experience in the module CO; 
You may have experience in SAP ABAP programming (debugging, reading programs...); 
You may have experience in the conversion from ERP to SAP 4/HANA; 
You enjoy occasional travel and communicate very well in English; 
You are able to understand complex interrelationships and have a strong analytical mindset; 
Furthermore, your character is characterized by initiative, team spirit and creativity. 
Loyal background, long term commitment. 
 Benefits: Motivating salary + extras. 
To be part of a new team. 
Strong company background. 
Home office: 3-4 times a week.

